                            <comment id="16119713" author="iamaleksey" created="Wed, 9 Aug 2017 10:53:01 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;If you have legacy pre-2.1 data shards lying around in sstables, this bug will hurt. One minor problem is that for people who don&apos;t, there will be a short period of digest mismatches during the minor upgrade from 3.0.prev to 3.0.next, but I don&apos;t see a way to avoid it.&lt;/p&gt;

